# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ALTERNATIVE DATA SOURCES (No API Keys Required!)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# We use these free alternatives instead of Reddit:
#
# 1. HACKER NEWS - Official Firebase API
#    - Completely free, no authentication needed
#    - Great for tech/finance/startup discussions
#    - API: https://hacker-news.firebaseio.com/v0/
#
# 2. RSS FEED AGGREGATOR - Multiple finance sources
#    - Reuters, BBC Business, MarketWatch, Yahoo Finance
#    - CoinTelegraph, CoinDesk (crypto)
#    - Kitco (gold/commodities)
#    - Pakistan news: Business Recorder, Dawn, Tribune, Geo
#    - No API keys needed - uses feedparser library
#
# Both scrapers are enabled by default in app/scrapers/scheduler.py

